videos.headline: Bronson makes difficult catch, scores 72-yard USF TD
videos.description: Ryeshene Bronson makes a highly contested catch and escapes two defenders to score a 72-yard USF touchdown.

videos.headline: Lewis tip-toes back of end zone for Cincinnati TD
videos.description: Cincinnati's Kahlil Lewis tip-toes in the back of the end zone to score a touchdown.

videos.headline: Warren dives for Cincinnati TD
videos.description: Michael Warren II makes the catch and dives to break the plane and score a Cincinnati touchdown.

videos.headline: USF's Wilcox makes diving catch for 38-yard TD
videos.description: Brett Kean connects with Mtichell Wilcox, who dives to make the 38-yard USF touchdown catch.

videos.headline: USF's McCants climbs ladder for 25-yard TD catch
videos.description: USF's Tyre McCants climbs the ladder against a Cincinnati defender to come down with the 25-yard touchdown catch.
